                      <span>2003-06-27</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book helped de-mystify ADO.NET for me.  Database access in .NET is a complex topic that was handled elegantly in this book. It's clear, concise, easy to read, and has a good mix of prose and step by step instruction that one needs to get a jump start with ADO.NET.  I recommed it highly.</span>
                  
              
